Issues/Links:
Ensure you have the deps mentioned here: https://kivy.org/doc/stable/installation/installation-linux-venvs.html#installation-in-venv

Bump the version of 
kivy to 1.10.1 because it has fixes for a breaking change in one of the SDL libs


